summary: This document appears to be a calendar entry or scheduling notice for a court conference in the Epstein case, scheduled for July 31, 2019, involving the U.S. Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York and the FBI.

events.title: Epstein Scheduling Conference
events.description: A court scheduling conference was held regarding the Epstein case, organized by the U.S. Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York, with the FBI listed as an attendee.

keyFacts: A scheduling conference for the Epstein case was held on July 31, 2019.
The conference was organized by the U.S. Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York (USANYS).
The FBI was listed as an attendee for the conference.
The document is a calendar entry created on July 23, 2019, and modified on July 31, 2019.
